  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      IOXSOR study's purpose to determine the frequency of non resolutive renal failure (estimated
      by the clearance of iohexol) at end of stay in ICU patients who have had acute renal failure
      episode.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
